OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,FThe all-Ireland Fleadh is to return to
OL,7,FBelfast for the second year in a row
OL,8,Fin 2027.
OL,10,FIt comes as the Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fcapital prepares to host the world's
OL,12,Flargest celebration of Irish music and
OL,13,Fculture for the first time this summer.
OL,15,FThe announcement was made following a
OL,16,Fmeeting of the Ardchomhairle of
OL,17,FComhaltas in Dublin on Saturday.
OL,19,FBelfast will also become the first
OL,20,Flocation in Northern Ireland to host
OL,21,Fthe event twice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
