PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,FThe showcase of traditional music,
OL,7,Fsong, dance and language, which will
OL,8,Ftake place from August 2 to 9, is
OL,9,Fexpected to attract more than 800,000.
OL,11,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill hailed
OL,12,Fthe "fantastic news".
OL,14,F"The Fleadh will be hosted in Belfast
OL,15,Fthis summer and return in 2027,
OL,16,Fbringing hundreds of thousands of
OL,17,Fvisitors from around the world to
OL,18,Fcelebrate the very best of Irish
OL,19,Fmusic, culture, and heritage," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@TO]vD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
