FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,F"This will also be a great boost for
OL,7,Four local economy. Beal Feirste will
OL,8,Fbe buzzing, and we can't wait to
OL,9,Fwelcome you all!"
OL,11,FSome of the artists involved in the
OL,12,F2026 event include musician Sharon
OL,13,FShannon and her Big Band who will
OL,14,Fheadline the main stage outside
OL,15,FBelfast City Hall on Sunday August 2.
OL,17,FOther acts performing on the famous
OL,18,FGig Rig stage for the opening ceremony
OL,19,Fwill be award-winning group Goitse,
OL,20,Fthe Blackwater Ceili Band and Belfast
OL,21,Fensemble McPeake.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,FThe line-up will also include a range
OL,7,Fof school choirs, as well as cross-
OL,8,Fcommunity and multicultural
OL,9,Fperformances, creating a day of free
OL,10,Fentertainment and setting the tone for
OL,11,Fa week of multi-generational shared
OL,12,Fcelebration across the city.
OL,14,FDeputy Lord Mayor of Belfast Paul
OL,15,FDoherty described it as a "tremendous
OL,16,Fhonour" for the city.
OL,18,F"We're delighted our city will host
OL,19,Fthe Fleadh again in 2027," he said.
OL,26,@wD@[OUxD@GO]zD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
