FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,F"It's a tremendous honour for Belfast
OL,7,Fand underscores its status as the
OL,8,Fisland's only Unesco City of Music.
OL,10,F"It allows us to build on 2026 and
OL,11,Ffurther strengthen Belfast's position
OL,12,Fas a vibrant, inclusive city that
OL,13,Fcelebrates its rich cultural heritage.
OL,15,F"The two-year staging will deliver a
OL,16,Fsubstantial tourism and economic
OL,17,Fimpact, supporting local businesses,
OL,18,Fhospitality providers and cultural
OL,19,Forganisations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
