FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,F"The opportunity to welcome so many
OL,7,Fartists and visitors to our city is
OL,8,Falready bringing great excitement and
OL,9,Fwill no doubt add to the atmosphere
OL,10,Fand energy of the week.
OL,12,F"We look forward to sharing everything
OL,13,FBelfast has to offer and to
OL,14,Fcelebrating together."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@VO]
