CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,FComhaltas Ceoltoiri Eireann praised
OL,7,Fthe partnership with Belfast City
OL,8,FCouncil and their host local branch,
OL,9,FArds CCE, saying that the combination
OL,10,Fof world-class international venues
OL,11,Fand specialist music hubs, unique
OL,12,Fstreet environments and strong
OL,13,Fcommunity support made the decision to
OL,14,Freturn to Belfast an easy one.
OL,16,FDr Labhras O Murchu, director-general
OL,17,Fof Comhaltas, said Belfast will
OL,18,Felevate the event to new heights.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
