PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,F"The decision to host the Fleadh in
OL,7,FBelfast again in 2027 reflects the
OL,8,Fscale of our ambition and the strength
OL,9,Fof our partnership with Belfast City
OL,10,FCouncil," he said.
OL,12,F"With world-class stages in the
OL,13,FWaterfront and Ulster Hall, Belfast is
OL,14,Fset to elevate the amazing
OL,15,Fperformances and atmosphere of Fleadh
OL,16,FCheoil na hEireann to new heights.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
