OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,F"It's clear the warmth of welcome that
OL,7,Fawaits in Belfast will create a
OL,8,Fnatural home for the event and we look
OL,9,Fforward to celebrating our 75th
OL,10,Fmilestone year in the city.
OL,12,F"We appreciate the work that Belfast
OL,13,FCity Council and Ards CCE have put
OL,14,Finto planning 2026 and for their 2027
OL,15,Fbid."
OL,17,FNiall McClean, chairman of Ards CCE,
OL,18,Fadded: "It's a privilege to host the
OL,19,Fevent in Belfast in both 2026 and 2027.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@EO]zD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
