FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772982672
OL,3,CAll-Ireland Fleadh to return to
OL,4,CBelfast in 2027
OL,6,F"Even before the first note has been
OL,7,Fplayed at Fleadh 2026, we've seen a
OL,8,Fremarkable surge in interest in Irish
OL,9,Ftraditional music, song and dance with
OL,10,Fincreased enrolment in classes
OL,11,Fparticularly around Belfast.
OL,13,F"The Fleadh is more than a festival,
OL,14,Fit's a catalyst to inspire older
OL,15,Fgenerations to pass on their skills
OL,16,Fand for new generations to carry these
OL,17,Ftimeless traditions forward.
OL,19,F"We continue to be delighted to be
OL,20,Fpart of this momentous opportunity for
OL,21,Fboth our organisation and for Belfast."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@gO]
